'From Squeak3.7 of ''4 September 2004'' [latest update: #5989] on 19 June 2008 at 4:55:10 pm'!!StrikeFont methodsFor: 'building' stamp: 'jmv 6/19/2008 16:55'!stripHighGlyphs	"Remove glyphs for characters above 128"	| i |	maxAscii _ 127.		xTable _ xTable copyFrom: 1 to: maxAscii + 3.	i _ xTable at: maxAscii + 1.	xTable at: maxAscii + 2 put: i.	xTable at: maxAscii + 3 put: i.	glyphs _ glyphs copy: (0@0 extent: i@glyphs height).	maxWidth _ 0.	2 to: xTable size do: [ :ii |		maxWidth _ maxWidth max: (xTable at: ii) - (xTable at: ii-1)-1 ].	characterToGlyphMap _ nil.	self reset! !